#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:8
msgid "Clean dangling package files, based on current repository data."
msgstr ""
"Bersihkan file paket yang menggantung berdasarkan data repositori saat ini."

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:10
msgid "Do not ask anything; use default answers automatically. Default: false"
msgstr ""
"Tidak menanyakan apa pun; gunakan jawaban default secara otomatis. Default: "
"false"

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:12
msgid "Run the clean process without actually removing files."
msgstr "Jalankan proses pembersihan tanpa benar-benar menghapus file."

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:14
msgid "List files during the cleaning process."
msgstr "Tampilkan daftar file selama proses pembersihan."

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:15
msgid ""
"Clean dangling package files based on current repository metadata.\n"
"\n"
"This command scans the mirror directory for 'repomd.xml' files, parses the\n"
"metadata files, and compares their content with files on disk. Files not\n"
"listed in the metadata and at least 2 days old are considered dangling.\n"
"\n"
"Then, it removes all dangling files from disk along with any associated databa"
"se entries.\n"
msgstr ""
"Bersihkan file paket yang menggantung berdasarkan metadata repositori saat "
"ini.\n"
"\n"
"Perintah ini memindai direktori mirror untuk file 'repomd.xml', mengurai\n"
"file metadata, dan membandingkan isinya dengan file yang ada di disk. File "
"yang tidak\n"
"tercantum dalam metadata dan berusia minimal 2 hari dianggap menggantung.\n"
"\n"
"Kemudian, semua file yang menggantung dihapus dari disk beserta entri basis "
"data yang terkait.\n"

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:29
msgid "Scanning the mirror directory for 'repomd.xml' files..."
msgstr "Memindai direktori mirror untuk file 'repomd.xml'..."

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:37
msgid "RMT found no repomd.xml files. Check if RMT is properly configured."
msgstr ""
"RMT tidak menemukan file repomd.xml. Periksa apakah RMT telah dikonfigurasi "
"dengan benar."

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:44
msgid "RMT found repomd.xml files: %{repomd_count}."
msgstr "RMT menemukan file repomd.xml: %{repomd_count}."

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:45
msgid ""
"Now, it will parse all repomd.xml files, search for dangling packages on disk "
"and clean them."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, semua file repomd.xml akan diurai, paket yang menggantung di "
"disk akan dicari dan dibersihkan."

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:49
msgid ""
"This can take several minutes. Would you like to continue and clean dangling p"
"ackages?"
msgstr ""
"Proses ini dapat memakan waktu beberapa menit. Apakah Anda ingin melanjutkan "
"dan membersihkan paket yang menggantung?"

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:51 ../lib/rmt/cli/repos.rb:40
msgid "Only '%{input}' will be accepted."
msgstr "Hanya '%{input}' yang akan diterima."

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:51 ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:57
msgid "yes"
msgstr "ya"

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:53 ../lib/rmt/cli/repos.rb:42
msgid "Enter a value:"
msgstr "Masukkan nilai:"

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:58 ../lib/rmt/cli/repos.rb:48
msgid "Clean cancelled."
msgstr "Pembersihan dibatalkan."

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:89
msgid "No dangling packages have been found!"
msgstr "Tidak ada paket yang menggantung ditemukan!"

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:97
msgid "Total: cleaned %{total_count} (%{total_size}), %{total_db_entries}."
msgstr "Total: %{total_count} dibersihkan (%{total_size}), %{total_db_entries}."

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:167
msgid "Directory: %{dir}"
msgstr "Direktori: %{dir}"

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:174
msgid "Cleaned '%{file_name}' (%{file_size}%{hardlink}), %{db_entries}."
msgstr "'%{file_name}' dibersihkan (%{file_size}%{hardlink}), %{db_entries}."

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:177
msgid "hardlink"
msgstr "hardlink"

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:184
msgid "Cleaned %{file_count_text} (%{total_size}), %{db_entries}."
msgstr "%{file_count_text} dibersihkan (%{total_size}), %{db_entries}."

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:198
msgid "%{count} file"
msgid_plural "%{count} files"
msgstr[0] "%{count} file"

#: ../lib/rmt/cli/clean.rb:202
msgid "%{db_entries} database entry"
msgid_plural "%{db_entries} database entries"
msgstr[0] "%{db_entries} entri basis data"

